snippet.title: Amber Heard and Corey Rae for L'Oréal Paris x Cannes 2019 (May 17, 2019)
snippet.description:
On the International Day Against Homophobia, Transphobia and Biphobia (May 17, 2019), Amber Heard invited Corey Rae to join her and L'Oréal Paris at the 2019 Cannes Film Festival. 
Corey is a transgender activist, model, and writer who works on shattering gender and sexuality stigmas around the transgender community. Learn more about the fight for equal rights at @free.equal (instagram account)
